="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/outrageous-spanish-fm-lashes-out-at-israeli-counterpart-katz-over-gracias-hamas-video/0000018f-b5b7-d33c-a5bf-ffb75e560000</guid></item><item><title>犹太纽约人纠结是否参加今年的以色列日游行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</link><description>被扣押在加沙的人质代表定于 6 月 2 日游行，但广受诟病的内塔尼亚胡政府的四名成员也将游行 — — 让许多外籍以色列人和自由派犹太人陷入困境</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/jewish-new-yorkers-wrestle-with-whether-to-march-in-this-years-israel-day-parade/0000018f-b491-dfc6-a3ef-b5ddd2540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</link><description>中士。 20 岁的贝扎莱尔·兹维·科瓦奇 (Betzalel Zvi Kovach) 上周三在加沙北部受伤，并于周日因伤死亡。中士。 20 岁的 Sahar Sudaei 周日在加沙北部被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 16:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-combat-last-week/0000018f-b59a-d08f-adcf-b7fa97b80000</guid></item><item><title>舒默参议员：不要邀请内塔尼亚胡。他不是你的盟友或朋友。他从来都不是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</link><description>向以色列坚定的民主党盟友传达的信息：不要邀请本杰明·内塔尼亚胡参加国会。他的唯一目的是在执行特朗普的命令时破坏美国总统乔·拜登的连任竞选</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 15:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/senator-schumer-dont-invite-netanyahu-hes-not-your-ally-or-your-friend-he-never-was/0000018f-b452-d390-ab8f-f5da4a7b0000</guid></i